name: TamaGoGo!
description:
You get only one gold coin and 1 minute to buy everything that's on the shopping list! -Controls- Move - WASD
Buy item - Left Mouse Button
Restart - R -How to play- You have a limited budget and time. Approach the stands and look for the cheapest offers.
When you have everything, return to the statue where you started! -Programs used-
  • Unity
  • Photoshop
  • Blender
  • Audacity
